  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.7">
<l>entai yēyeṉṟu memperu māṉeṉṟuñ</l>
<l>cintai yuḷvaippaṉ colluvaṉ pāviyē</l>
<l>ṉentai yemperu māṉeṉṟu vāṉavar</l>
<l>cintai yuḷvaittuc collumcel vaṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I put [him] into my thoughts [and] speak [of him]</l>
<l>as “our father” and “our lord”, I who am a sinner,</l>
<l>– of the lord whom the celestials put in [their] thoughts,</l>
<l>[and] call “our father, our lord”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
